Version 1.0.1.

	Added support for Russian letters 'yo small' and 'yo capital'
	(unicode characters 0451 and 0401 respectively). Thanks to
	Leonid Pauzner <leonid@pauzner.mccme.ru> for pointing me
	to correct recoding tables.

Version 1.0.2.

	Minor bug fixes and improvements. Thanks again to Leonid Pauzner.

Version 1.1.

	Fixed bugs introduced in version 1.0.1 that prevented emagic from
	proper encoding recognition.

	Added external conversion tables support.
	
	Added some more sophisticated euristics to improve encoding
	recognition.

	Iluminated inefective conversion sequences, for example
	koi->iso, iso->win is the same as koi->win
	

